{"id": 657, "genre": 1001, "title": "天这么冷，\b你为什么不戴帽子？", "description": "一种我无法参与的时尚。", "record_count": 5131, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703130138OoxesIUrkcjWTHfX.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-11-25T11:46:45Z", "options": [{"id": 28672, "content": "我戴?", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114479}, {"id": 38913, "content": "脸皮薄，不好意思装逼。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 403499}, {"id": 28675, "content": "我戴帽子，并且我有很多帽子！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 46182}, {"id": 30723, "content": "一般在外面戴了帽子 注定今天不能摘下来..毕竟不是在电影里面...", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 335706}, {"id": 31748, "content": "怕热", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 340271}, {"id": 28677, "content": "不喜欢就是不喜欢~~", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 92247}, {"id": 44549, "content": "头小很难选到合适的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1290302}, {"id": 28678, "content": "戴帽子对于我们这些齐刘海简直就是噩梦", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 301421}, {"id": 28680, "content": "招风耳不适合戴帽子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 326220}, {"id": 42764, "content": "脸太瘦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 289868}, {"id": 28685, "content": "脑袋大  母上剖腹产的我", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 299799}, {"id": 30733, "content": "懒", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 330126}, {"id": 28687, "content": "前提是，广东要有冬天……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 319487}, {"id": 28688, "content": "帽子摆在架子上最好看", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 26306}, {"id": 28689, "content": "就是因为穷啊……哪来那么多为什么……，d", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 326251}, {"id": 28690, "content": "头大脸胖 ┐=͟͟͞͞(￣ー￣)┌ ", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 324121}, {"id": 28691, "content": "头大脸大 简直丑哭", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 161804}, {"id": 28693, "content": "会被北京的大风吹走", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 303279}, {"id": 28694, "content": "因为找不到好看的帽子，要绿色的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 258300}, {"id": 29206, "content": "头大，", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 298916}, {"id": 28696, "content": "因为只有一双鞋！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 250764}, {"id": 28698, "content": "头发会油", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 326283}, {"id": 29210, "content": "还没有遇见一顶合适的帽子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 329812}, {"id": 28699, "content": "头发太软，帽子摘掉，头发被压成一个帽子形状紧贴头皮。囧o(╯□╰)o！", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 324740}, {"id": 28700, "content": "暖和的时候忘记买，冷的时候又来不及了。所以没有帽子。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 326327}, {"id": 28701, "content": "长得不够帅", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 216215}, {"id": 30749, "content": "公务员不成文的规定，不戴帽子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 335781}, {"id": 28703, "content": "毕竟国土风情有分别。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 39258}, {"id": 28707, "content": "拿下来不觉得冷么", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 184083}, {"id": 28708, "content": "毛线帽子光好看了，但是防风效果差", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 282776}, {"id": 31268, "content": "没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 337613}, {"id": 28709, "content": "你是北方人吗？我们还穿着短袖，带帽子得多热", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 326436}, {"id": 32805, "content": "谁说我不戴", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 346455}, {"id": 28710, "content": "从小都没戴过，没这习惯啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 312598}, {"id": 31014, "content": "因为媳妇儿不让我戴帽子", "image": "img/option/option/201607021826584Qm3N9jPsbDTOGxI.jpg", "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 336685}, {"id": 33318, "content": "脑袋大！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 311346}, {"id": 28712, "content": "发型!发型!发型!重要的事情说三遍", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 191284}, {"id": 28713, "content": "头太小，在帽子里来回转圈", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 326467}, {"id": 28714, "content": "头大,戴不下啊！多年的痛?", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 255269}, {"id": 28970, "content": "没有看到合适的帽子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 328243}, {"id": 28715, "content": "我没有帽子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 315330}, {"id": 30507, "content": "因为丑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 94536}, {"id": 39211, "content": "因为所在的城市，戴上帽子会显得是神经病", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 406137}, {"id": 28972, "content": "带着想小2B", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 328253}, {"id": 32044, "content": "怕头发乱了、摘掉后被认为是疯子", "image": "img/option/option/20160702182628Zmchbsw0Ui3dKal7.jpg", "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 306521}, {"id": 35372, "content": "hold不住，而已", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 370293}, {"id": 28717, "content": "怎么说呢，淘宝上卖的帽子质量太差", 